headline: Henry Schein Medical Honors Women Trailblazers in Athletic Training on National Girls and Women in Sports Day 2025
summary: MELVILLE, N.Y., February 05, 2025--Henry Schein Medical, the U.S. medical business of Henry Schein, Inc. (Nasdaq: HSIC), is paying tribute to women athletic trainers (ATs) during today’s celebration of National Girls and Women in Sports Day 2025.
